OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with plenty of sunshine
OL,7,Fthis evening, then staying dry and
OL,8,Fclear overnight. Some mist and fog
OL,9,Fpatches are likely to form in some
OL,10,Fprone rural spots during the early
OL,11,Fhours. Light and variable winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FMorning mist and fog patches
OL,14,Fquickly clearing to leave a fine and
OL,15,Fvery warm day, with plenty of
OL,16,Fsunshine. Perhaps a little cloud
OL,17,Freturning to parts of Cumbria at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
